딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">  - 서울캠퍼스 : 관리처 시설안전팀(내선 ☎ 8569, 8568)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">  - 고양캠퍼스 : BMC행정처 BMC종합행정실(내선 ☎ 5453)</span></span></p>",
